quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  9,7,"Ko honno ahadi woniranta sirkooɓe ɓen ka Alla e ka Nulaaɗo Makko on? Si wanaa ɓen ɓe ahoduɗon ka Juulirde hormanteere. Fodde hiɓe ñinnani on, ñinnanee ɓe. Pellet, Alla no yiɗi gomɗuɓe ɓen"
  9,8,"Ko honno si ɓe foolii on, ɓe aynitataa e mooɗon enɗam wanaa ahadi?! Hiɓe weltinira on kunndule maɓɓe, ɓerɗe maɓɓe ɗen saloo; ko ɓuri ɗuuɗude e maɓɓe kadi ko faasiqiiɓe"
  9,9,"Ɓe waɗtitirii Aayeeje Alla ɗen coggu fanɗungu ɓe sakkii(faddii) e laawol Makko ngol. Pellet, kamɓe ko ɓe gollaynoo kon na bonii"
  9,10,Ɓe aynitataa e gomɗinɗo enɗam wanaa ahadi. Ko ɓen woni jaggitooɓe ɓen
  9,11,"Si ɓe tuubii, ɓe ñinnii julde ɓe tottii zakka, haray ko ɓe siɗɓe mo'on ka diina. Meɗen fensitana Aayeeje ɗen yimɓe annduɓe"
  9,12,"Si ɓe firtii goondooje maɓɓe ɗen ɓaawo ahadi maɓɓe ndin ɓe yuwi e diina mon kan, haray haɓee hooreeɓe keeferaaku ɓen -tawde kamɓe ahadi alanaa ɓe - belajo'o, ɓe haɗitoto"
  9,13,"E on haɓataa yimɓe firtuɓe goondooje maɓɓe, ɓe himmiri yaltinngol Nulaaɗo on, ko kamɓe kadi adii on ɗaɓɓitude? E on hulay ɓe?! Ko Alla ɓuri hanndude Mo huloton si on laatike gomɗimɓe"